cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.CV, cs.RO 

This paper is about reinforcement learning for a complex game, StarCraft II. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI, which covers topics related to artificial intelligence and machine learning. The paper also discusses the use of hierarchical reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (machine learning). The paper also mentions the use of computer vision techniques for game state representation, which falls under the category of cs.CV (computer vision). The paper also discusses the use of a curriculum transfer learning algorithm, which falls under the category of cs.GT (game theory). Finally, the paper mentions the use of a two-layer hierarchical architecture, which falls under the category of cs.RO (robotics).
